  "full_name": "nashsu/freeaskinternet",
  "description": "FreeAskInternet is a completely free, PRIVATE and LOCALLY running search aggregator \u0026 answer generate using MULTI LLMs, without GPU needed. The user can ask a question and the system will  make a multi engine search and combine the search result to LLM and generate the answer based on search results. It's all FREE to use. ",
  "description_ja": "FreeAskInternet は GPU 不要で完全無料・プライベート・ローカル動作の検索アグリゲーター＆回答生成ツール。マルチ LLM 使用。ユーザーが質問すると複数エンジンで検索し、結果を LLM に渡して回答を生成する",
